# Project Structure

This project follows a specific organizational structure. **Always** maintain these conventions.

## Directory Structure

```
howtowincapitalism/
├── .cursor/rules/        # AI assistant rules (this folder)
├── _docs/                # Human-readable documentation
│   ├── devlog/           # Daily development logs
│   ├── status_reports/   # Project status reports
│   ├── ARCHITECTURE.md   # Technical architecture
│   ├── PROJECT_POLICIES.md # Standards and conventions
│   └── README.md         # Documentation index
├── _work_efforts/        # Task tracking (Johnny Decimal)
│   ├── 00-09_meta/       # Organization, indexes
│   ├── 10-19_development/# Dev tasks, architecture
│   ├── 20-29_features/   # Feature work
│   └── 30-39_infrastructure/ # Deployment, CI/CD
├── src/                  # Source code
│   ├── components/       # Astro components (atomic design)
│   ├── content/          # MDX content pages
│   ├── lib/              # Utilities and tools
│   ├── pages/            # Route pages
│   └── styles/           # CSS
├── scripts/              # Build/deploy scripts
├── public/               # Static assets
├── README.md             # Project overview
└── AGENTS.md             # AI assistant instructions
```

## Folder Purposes

| Folder | Purpose | What Goes Here |
|--------|---------|----------------|
| `_docs/` | Documentation | Devlogs, architecture, policies, guides |
| `_work_efforts/` | Task tracking | Work effort files (Johnny Decimal) |
| `src/lib/tools/` | Utilities | Reusable TypeScript/JS utilities |
| `scripts/` | Automation | Build, deploy, generator scripts |

## Rules

### 1. Never Create These Folders
- `_dev/` — Use `src/lib/tools/` for development utilities
- `utils/` at root — Use `src/lib/` instead
- Nested date folders like `2025/12/` — Use flat structure with dated filenames

### 2. Always Update Documentation
When making significant changes:
- Update relevant `_docs/` file
- Update or create work effort in `_work_efforts/`
- Update devlog if in active development session

### 3. File Naming
All filenames must be self-descriptive without relying on folder path.

| ❌ Bad | ✅ Good |
|--------|---------|
| `09.md` | `2025-12-09_devlog.md` |
| `index.md` (nested) | `feature-index.md` |
| `utils.ts` | `decision-matrix-utils.ts` |

**Exceptions:** `README.md`, `index.mdx` (for routes), standard config files.

### 4. Date Format
Use ISO 8601: `YYYY-MM-DD`

Examples:
- `2025-12-09_devlog.md`
- `2025-12_monthly-summary.md`
